nk:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531626\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531626\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rjc1665702973286.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjc1665702973286.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjc1665702973286.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rjc1665702973286\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Sybase Numeric, Text, and Image Fields\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__section_t5y_422_kcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163434e54\">Numeric Fields </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__p_d61091e1_d61092e1_d61093e1\">Numerics are supported with a Uniface precision limit\n            of 32 digits. Uniface precision differs from Sybase precision in that Uniface precision\n            counts the number of characters and Sybase precision counts the number of digits; that\n            is, Uniface precision includes the decimal point and the Sybase precision does not. If\n            no scale is required, the Uniface precision is the same as the Sybase precision.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__table_d5405e1_d5406e1_d5407e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Scaling with Sybase Numerics</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__table_d5405e1_d5406e1_d5407e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__table_d5405e1_d5406e1_d5407e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sybase</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjc1665702973286__table_d5405e1_d5406e1_d5407e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">N4.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjc1665702973286__table_d5405e1_d5406e1_d5407e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Numeric(3,2)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjc1665702973286__table_d5405e1_d5406e1_d5407e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">N4.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjc1665702973286__table_d5405e1_d5406e1_d5407e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Numeric(4,0)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__p_d61094e1_d61095e1_d61096e1\">The model must always contain precision values which\n            are larger than the corresponding scale value. For example, fields with Uniface packing\n            code N2.2 are illegal because the Sybase precision must be greater than or equal to the\n            scale.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__p_d61097e1_d61098e1_d61099e1\">Fields with packing codes N32, O31, O32, P16 and Q16\n            can drop significant digits if used to store the maximum number of digits allowed. This\n            is due to the internal remapping and conversion which takes place before Uniface can map\n            the value to a Numeric.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__section_bgh_q22_kcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163434e133\">Text and Image Fields</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__p_d61103e1_d61104e1_d61105e1\">In some situations, the Fetch request only needs\n            information about the Text or Image fields, but not the actual segmented fields\n            themselves. In these situations, only the first four bytes of each field are retrieved\n            during each Uniface Fetch request.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjc1665702973286__p_d61106e1_d61107e1_d61108e1\">To fetch only the first four bytes of the Text or\n            Image field, the Sybase SQL Server text size is set to four during the Fetch request so\n            that the Sybase SQL Server only returns four bytes.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cug1665702973144.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Sybase Data Packing</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531626\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531626\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Sybase Numeric, Text, and Image Fields Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sybase Numeric, Text, and Image Fields Numeric Fields Numerics are supported with a Uniface precision limit of 32 digits. Uniface precision differs from Sybase precision in that Uniface precision counts the number of characters and Sybase precision counts the number of digits; that is, Uniface precision includes the decimal point and the Sybase precision does not. If no scale is required, the Uniface precision is the same as the Sybase precision. Table 1. Scaling with Sybase Numerics Uniface Sybase N4.2 Numeric(3,2) N4.0 Numeric(4,0) The model must always contain precision values which are larger than the corresponding scale value. For example, fields with Uniface packing code N2.2 are illegal because the Sybase precision must be greater than or equal to the scale. Fields with packing codes N32, O31, O32, P16 and Q16 can drop significant digits if used to store the maximum number of digits allowed. This is due to the internal remapping and conversion which takes place before Uniface can map the value to a Numeric. Text and Image Fields In some situations, the Fetch request only needs information about the Text or Image fields, but not the actual segmented fields themselves. In these situations, only the first four bytes of each field are retrieved during each Uniface Fetch request. To fetch only the first four bytes of the Text or Image field, the Sybase SQL Server text size is set to four during the Fetch request so that the Sybase SQL Server only returns four bytes. Related Links Sybase Data Packing Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}